566
00:39:27,970 --> 00:39:30,320
He will be staying at home for the next few days.

567
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:32,680
Sure thing!

568
00:39:32,680 --> 00:39:34,420
That is good, too.

569
00:39:36,870 --> 00:39:39,610
All right, all right. Hurry up and go rest.

570
00:39:39,610 --> 00:39:41,510
