- Let's go.

571
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:50,460
Right now, you should be at ease. Right?

572
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:54,580
Anyway, this matter is my fault.

573
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:57,930
I should have watched you 24/7.

574
00:39:57,930 --> 00:40:00,740
