576
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:07,780
When I was at the hospital, you didn't answer a single call of mine!

577
00:40:08,850 --> 00:40:12,330
I was in a rush to look for jobs.

578
00:40:12,330 --> 00:40:15,890
